Summary: I saw the object in a photo I took from the Cemetery
divs: Sighting DetailsI was walking through the cemetery taking photos of damage from the Earthquake. I took a short series of photos and when I looked through them later there was an abnormally in two photos. The object doesn't line up with any know flight pattern of airplanes in the country. I have attached the photo to this report
